      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk man. i was just looking at the stars and thinking about how huge everything is. everything we do, every single thing anyone has ever done... it's all just going to be swallowed by entropy anyway. in a few billion years there's not even gonna be light left. it feels like everything is just a massive, pointless joke. why even bother trying to fix anything or be anything if none of it actually matters in the end?",
